svg.text: What would you say to your party guests? In pairs, take turns practicing what to say to your
guests at a party, based on the following prompts.
Explain that the party is to:
welcome Little Chen back from a long trip
send off Little Tian on a long trip
celebrate Little Bai having found a good job
Ask the guests not to stand on ceremony, enjoy the food and have a good time:
Offer to help and take care of each other to a new acquaintance:
